## FEATURES

━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

**▸ ADVANCED AIMBOT SYSTEM**
- Perfect accuracy with adjustable lock strength
- Smooth aiming that looks natural
- Configurable Field of View (FOV)
- Multiple hitbox selection (head, chest, body, limbs)
- Priority targeting (closest, crosshair, lowest health)
- Visibility checking to avoid shooting through walls
- Flashbang immunity option

**▸ INTELLIGENT TRIGGERBOT**
- Automatically fires when crosshair is on enemy
- Adjustable trigger delay (0-500ms)
- Configurable shot range
- Multiple hitbox options
- Burst fire mode for rifles
- Key binding for manual override
- Safe mode to avoid detection

**▸ COMPLETE RECOIL CONTROL**
- Zero recoil on all weapons
- Spread reduction for perfect accuracy
- Weapon-specific profiles (AK-47, M4, AWP, etc.)
- Visual recoil compensation crosshair
- Adjustable compensation strength
- Pattern learning for perfect spray control

**▸ VISUAL AIM INDICATORS**
- Target circles on locked enemies
- Color-coded target highlighting
- Enemy health bars
- Distance indicators
- Snap lines to targets
- Customizable colors and opacity

